title: Shapeshifters - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/13/22
itunes:title: Shapeshifters - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/13/22
description:
George Noory and paranormal investigator John Kachuba discuss his research into the legend of shapeshifters, humans who have the ability to transform into animals or other creatures, and how figures like Dracula, Superman and even Jesus could be considered shapeshifters.
